      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$19<span class="accent">/mo</span></div><div class="stat-label">Cheapest full-feature GBP analytics (Localo)</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$49<span class="accent">/mo</span></div><div class="stat-label">theStacc Local SEO · analytics + automation</div></div>
