        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Every other tool on this list shows you your GBP data and leaves the improvement to you. theStacc shows you the data and automatically does the work: weekly GBP posts published to your profile, AI-generated review responses drafted and posted, citation submissions across 50+ directories, and local content published to your website. The Local SEO module at $49/month is the only GBP tool in this category that closes the gap between knowing your ranking and actually moving it. Bundle with Blog SEO ($99) for 30 blog articles per month too.</p>
