            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Review monitoring with automated AI response drafts</h4>
              <p>Every new review is detected. Responses are drafted in your brand voice. One-click approval or full auto-response mode. Review response rate goes from 0% to near-100% without manual effort.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Citation management across 50+ directories</h4>
              <p>Consistent NAP (name, address, phone) across the major directories that influence local rankings. Submission and monitoring handled automatically.</p>
            </div>
