            <div>
              <h4>Honest con: not the deepest standalone GBP analytics dashboard</h4>
              <p>If you want geo-grid heatmaps across a 5-mile radius with 50-point grid scans, theStacc's analytics aren't as granular as Local Falcon or BrightLocal's dedicated tracking dashboards. For analytics depth alone, pair theStacc with Local Falcon ($24.99/month) for the most complete picture.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/checkout/" class="btn btn-primary"><span>Start the $1 trial <span class="arrow">→</span></span></a>
          <a href="/modules/local-seo/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-left: 12px;">See Local SEO module</a>
