      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#2 · $39–$59/MO · FULL LOCAL ANALYTICS SUITE</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">BrightLocal — Best standalone GBP analytics platform for local businesses and agencies</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For agencies and local businesses that need the most complete GBP analytics suite — geo-grid tracking, GBP audit, citation monitoring, review aggregation, and competitor benchmarking.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">BrightLocal is the most complete GBP analytics platform on the market. The geo-grid rank tracker scans your Maps ranking at dozens of geographic points across a customizable radius and displays the result as a color-coded heatmap. The GBP audit scores your profile against local ranking factors. Review analytics aggregate from Google, Yelp, and Facebook. Citation monitoring tracks your NAP consistency across directories. For agencies needing to report on GBP performance for multiple clients, BrightLocal has the best combination of data depth and white-label reporting.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Geo-grid rank tracking with color-coded heatmaps</h4><p>The flagship feature. See exactly where you rank in Maps across a customizable geographic radius. Identifies ranking blind spots that aggregate position data hides.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>GBP audit with actionable optimization checklist</h4><p>Scores your profile against local ranking factors. Flags missing categories, incomplete attributes, photo count benchmarks, and description gaps. Each issue links to a specific fix.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Multi-platform review aggregation</h4><p>Google, Yelp, Facebook, and 10+ other platforms in one dashboard. Review monitoring without checking 6 different tabs manually.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: analytics only — no GBP posting or content automation</h4><p>BrightLocal shows you what's happening but doesn't automatically do the work that improves your rankings. You still need to post to GBP, respond to reviews, and build citations manually (or pay BrightLocal's managed services team separately).</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-3" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#3 · $24.99/MO · GEO-GRID MAPS TRACKING</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Local Falcon — Best geo-grid Maps rank tracking tool</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For local businesses and agencies that need precise geo-grid Maps ranking visualization — seeing exactly where you're visible and where you disappear across a geographic radius.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Local Falcon does one thing: shows your Google Maps ranking across a geographic grid. The visual heatmap is the best in the category — clear, color-coded, and immediately actionable. Run a scan, see a map of where you rank across your service area, identify the neighborhoods where you're invisible, and target local SEO efforts there first. The pricing is based on scan credits — you pay for the scans you run, not a flat monthly fee.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Best visual geo-grid heatmap for Maps rankings</h4><p>The clearest, most actionable visualization of geographic Maps rankings in the category. Color-coded from green (#1–3) to red (#10+) across every grid point.</p></div></li>
