          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Affordable credit-based pricing</h4><p>$24.99/month for credits. Only pay for the scans you run. Businesses that scan monthly spend less than businesses running daily tracking.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: geo-grid only — no performance metrics, no review analytics</h4><p>Local Falcon tracks Maps rankings. It doesn't track impressions, calls, clicks, reviews, or citations. For a complete GBP analytics picture, you need BrightLocal or a combination of tools.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-4" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#4 · $19–$69/MO · BUDGET GBP TRACKING</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Localo — Best budget GBP analytics and local rank tracking</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For small businesses and solo operators that need GBP audit scores and local rank tracking at the lowest price point in the category.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Localo (formerly known as SurferLocal) combines GBP profile scoring, local rank tracking, and some competitor visibility at a price that undercuts most alternatives. The GBP audit score identifies optimization gaps with actionable recommendations. Local rank tracking shows position trends over time. For businesses that don't need geo-grid visualization but want to track whether their local SEO efforts are moving the needle, Localo is the best value at this price.</p>
