          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Local rank tracking at $19/month — cheapest legitimate option</h4><p>Track your local keyword rankings over time. See whether this month's GBP posts and optimizations improved your position for target queries.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Competitor visibility data</h4><p>See which competitors rank above you and what their profiles look like. Basic benchmarking for businesses that need directional data without full competitor analytics.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: no geo-grid tracking and limited review analytics</h4><p>Localo tracks aggregate local rankings, not geo-grid Maps positions. Review analytics is basic. For the full analytics picture, BrightLocal or Local Falcon cover the gaps.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
